---
title: Roast Veggie & Bean Ribollita with Plant-Based Pesto & Garlic Ciabatta
description: This hearty plant-based veggie soup that's hailed from Tuscany is just what the doctor ordered. With tender cannellini
beans, a finishing of basil pesto and crusty ciabatta, this is the type of recipe that’ll soon become a dinnertime staple.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
